Unicron:



Unicron sensed the almost constant flow of Predacons who seemed intent on 
helping their sworn enemies the Maximals survive when they could just simply 
crush them.  Stupidity like that would be one of many reasons the 
Cybertronians unloyal to him would be executed like dogs.

He activated a comm. transmission to the Ramora.  "Hell Beast, this is 
Unicron.  The battle at the CF's tides are turning.  I urge you and your 
forces to get to the Cybertronian Fire and attack.  I also urge you 
to...(I'll e-mail you the plan later JP).  I suggest you hurry."
